abstract: Corinna da Fonseca-Wollheim reviews final concert in National Council Auditions at Metropolitan Opera House.

headline.print_headline: Big Room, Big Voice, Big Prizes
headline.main: Review: Five Young Winners, and Others, at National Council Auditions

snippet: At the Metropolitan Opera House, top prizes went to Sol Jin, Yelena Dyachek, Jakub Jozef Orlinski, Emily D’Angelo and Sean Michael Plumb.
lead_paragraph: At the Metropolitan Opera House, top prizes went to Sol Jin, Yelena Dyachek, Jakub Jozef Orlinski, Emily D’Angelo and Sean Michael Plumb.
